title: This is why I make music.
description:
Last Friday my album came out. So many of you have taken the time to say what these songs mean to you. I’m so grateful that you have. And I wanted to share a little bit more about the story behind it. Thank you for listening, and thanks to all the people who brought Gardenview into this world!

Vinyl & more at http://NatalyDawnMusic.com 

Credits:
Directed & Edited by Athena Wheaton
Studio Videography by Ryan Blewett
Additional Videography by Athena Wheaton
With gratitude to: John Schroeder, Ross Garren, Eliana Athayde, Kyle Crane, Caleb Parker, Henri Cash, Pierre de Reeder, Alexandria Allen, and the Pomplamoose team.
